Successful Voter Registration Drive at Juneteenth Festival by The Young Professionals of the Urban League of Palm Beach County

The Young Professionals of the Urban League of Palm Beach County made a significant impact at the Juneteenth Festival by hosting a live voter registration drive. The event was a major success, attracting a large number of festival attendees who eagerly registered to vote.
